  "difficultyLevel": 4,
  "lyrics": "So we say what you mean, do you really mean what you say? When it means you wake up today you'll take gratitude for you Do you say what's true or is it just your view? Take a second to understand something new Take a second to see a different view of you Do you ask yourself why or say why you're feeling all you do? You could just say it, just say it, all you feel inside Yeah you could just say it, just say it, let yourself start to divide High up in the world I think I'm the perfect place where we all could just rest For one second more to ignore, and the demons are at your door So you should just say it, instead of asking someone's why Yeah you should just say it, for you, and all you wanna feel too You should just say it, say it, say it to me nicely and soft Yeah say it to me, say it to me like we were friends again Like this enemy sinking from the end www.mooji.org",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 27.8799991607666,
      "text": "So we say what you mean, do you really mean what you say?",
      "start": 19.299999237060547
    },
    {
      "end": 45.7400016784668,
      "text": "When it means you wake up today you'll take gratitude for you",
      "start": 38.880001068115234
    },
    {
      "end": 57.5,
      "text": "Do you say what's true or is it just your view?",
      "start": 46.7400016784668
    },
    {
      "end": 68.4800033569336,
      "text": "Take a second to understand something new Take a second to see a different view of you",
      "start": 59.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 76.81999969482422,
      "text": "Do you ask yourself why or say why you're feeling all you do?",
      "start": 68.4800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 86.12000274658203,
      "text": "You could just say it, just say it, all you feel inside",
      "start": 77.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 97.22000122070312,
      "text": "Yeah you could just say it, just say it, let yourself start to divide",
      "start": 86.12000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 105.81999969482422,
      "text": "High up in the world I think I'm the perfect place where we all could just rest",
      "start": 97.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 115.58000183105469,
      "text": "For one second more to ignore, and the demons are at your door",
      "start": 106.73999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 124.27999877929688,
      "text": "So you should just say it, instead of asking someone's why",
      "start": 115.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 135.3000030517578,
      "text": "Yeah you should just say it, for you, and all you wanna feel too",
      "start": 125.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 141.02000427246094,
      "text": "You should just say it, say it, say it to me nicely and soft",
      "start": 135.4199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 148.44000244140625,
      "text": "Yeah say it to me, say it to me like we were friends again",
      "start": 141.5399932861328
    },
    {
      "end": 153.22000122070312,
      "text": "Like this enemy sinking from the end",
      "start": 148.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 192.3800048828125,
      "text": "www.mooji.org",
      "start": 192.17999267578125
    }
  ],
